                  "type": "note",
                  "id": "m6ZTs",
                  "name": "noteNav",
                  "width": 400,
                  "height": 240,
                  "content": "component/BottomNavBar → anPPw\n\nTheme axis: selected-tab\nValid values: \"home\" | \"words\" | \"mypage\"\nNo theme set → all tabs unselected\n\nUsage: <ref ref=\"anPPw\" theme={\"selected-tab\": \"words\"} />\n\nVariables that drive the swap:\n- $tab.<tab>.pillFill (background of tab pill)\n- $tab.<tab>.iconFill (icon + label color)\n\nDescendant override paths (instance customization):\n- WNaDT: notification badge frame (words tab) — set enabled:false to hide\n- WNaDT child text: badge count\n- l2a/l2b/l2c: tab labels (홈, 단어, 마이) — content override per locale"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
