                  "name": "splitNote",
                  "width": 420,
                  "height": 240,
                  "content": "component/SplitButton → 7fjpg\n\nTwo-zone primary action button. Both zones share $accent.primary fill; vertical divider on right edge of editZone (#FFFFFF30) separates them.\n\nDescendant override paths (ref+'/<id>'):\n- KAq5T: editZone container (52w). To hide: set enabled:false (left zone disappears, mainZone fills full width)\n- FaldF: edit icon (lucide 'pen') — override iconFontName per action\n- 2a0cL: mainZone container (fill_container)\n- z5b93: main icon (lucide 'plus') — override iconFontName or set enabled:false\n- gGsoD: main label text (담기)\n\nSource: Z9Q3a (splitBtn) from screen q96HS '2. Word Lookup — 담은 적 없는 단어'."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
